                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Synagogue Chambers</placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philad.</placeName>\n                                        <date>Shebat 4<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 5611</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <date>January 7<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> 1851</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>Dear Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your Letter of <date>8<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi>\n                                                  Nov</date> addressed to the<lb/> wardens of our\n                                        congregation was received and sub=<lb/>mitted to the Parnass\n                                        and Adjunta who compose the<lb/> Board of Managers, it\n                                        should have met with<lb/> an earlier answer but for a\n                                        pressure of business<lb/> engagements, and in Conformity\n                                        with your request<lb/> I proceed to give you as nearly as\n                                        possible the information<lb/> requested,—The office of Hazan\n                                        is vacant, and the<lb/> congregation have agreed to go into\n                                        an election for one<lb/> on the <date>13<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                                                  >th</hi> April</date>, The term of service was to\n                                        have been<lb/> originally ten years but owing to particular\n                                        &amp; peculiar cir<lb/>=cumstances not necessary to be here\n                                        narrated I am<lb/> of the opinion that no new incumbent will\n                                        be engaged<lb/> at the outset for more than Three years and\n                                        that the<lb/> ten years term will be rescinded. The salary\n                                        to a<lb/> single man will be $1300, to a married man\n                                        seventeen<lb/> hundred Dollars ($1700) per annum. The Hazan\n                                        will<lb/> be expected to say all the usual prayers of\n                                                  <date>sabbath</date><lb/> eve, morning, afternoon\n                                        &amp; conclusion service, and on<lb/> holy-days &amp;\n                                        festivals with no other aid except in the<lb/> Haphtara\n                                        &amp; on <date>Kippur day</date> , it is not by law any\n                                        part<lb/> of his duty to deliver English discourses but as\n                                        it has<lb/> been for many years the custom to do so, an\n                                        occa<lb/>=sional address or moral lecture in English will\n                                        be<lb/> expected. The Hazan is to perform all marriage\n                                        and<lb/> funeral services in the congregation and to\n                                        attend<lb/> the seven days mourning service, he will be\n                                        per=<lb/>=mitted to keep school and indeed his ability to\n                                        teach</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3d50gh6v/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
